quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,When the earth is shaken with its (final) earthquake
  99,2,and the earth threw out its burdens
  99,3,"and the human being said: “What (has gone wrong) with it?”"
  99,4,That Day it will narrate (all the) news available with it
  99,5,Because your Nourisher-Sustainer inspired unto it
  99,6,That Day mankind will proceed in groups so that they may be shown their deeds
  99,7,"So whosoever does good of the weight of a particle, he shall see it"
  99,8,"And whosoever does evil of the weight of a particle, he shall see it"